19/01/2010
TIRANA, Albania -- The head of the European Commission (EC) office in Tirana, Helmuth Lohan, said on Monday (January 18th) that the EU will provide support to rebuild the Shkodra region, devastated this month by floods. At a session on Monday, Albania's parliament adopted a resolution to assist regions affected by flooding and compensate families that suffered losses. (Deutche Welle, Top Channel, Shekulli, Ora News, Lajmi Fundit, Telegrafi - 18/01/10)
